                            </defs>
                            <rect id="base-litter" x="0" y="0" width="100%" height="100%"></rect>
                        </svg>
                        <div class="body">
                            <p>
                                The quality of water in the Victorian waterways is majorly affected due to the mindless disposal of litter.
                            </p>
