            </div>
            <div class="hidden-lg hidden-md col-sm-3 hidden-xs"></div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                <figure>
                    <div class="media" id="stormwater-box"></div>
                    <figcaption>
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" version="1.1" preserveAspectRatio="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <defs>
                                <mask id="mask-stormwater" x="0" y="0" width="100%" height="100%">
                                    <rect id="alpha" x="0" y="0" width="100%" height="100%"></rect>
                                    <text class="title" dx="50%" dy="2.5em">STORMWATER</text>
                                    <text class="title" dx="50%" dy="3.5em">POLLUTION</text>
                                </mask>
                            </defs>
                            <rect id="base-stormwater" x="0" y="0" width="100%" height="100%"></rect>
                        </svg>
                        <div class="body">
                            <p>
                                Every year a large amount of pollutants gets carried into the drains due to the rain, making the water unusable for various purposes.
                            </p>
